\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{\bm{z}}$
\end_inset

 is parallel to the direction of the ordered moment: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\bm{z}=R\tilde{\bm{z}}.
\end{equation}

\end_inset

